nl_querry: How many students in the Student_Club are from the College of Engineering?
llm_querry: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT m.member_id) FROM member m JOIN major ma ON m.link_to_major = ma.major_id WHERE ma.college = 'College of Engineering';
gold_querry: SELECT COUNT(T1.member_id) FROM member AS T1 INNER JOIN major AS T2 ON T1.link_to_major = T2.major_id WHERE T2.college = 'College of Engineering'
